title: Happy Valley Season 1 Complete
description:
Happy Valley is a British crime drama television series filmed and set in the Calder Valley. The series stars Sarah Lancashire and Siobhan Finneran. Also starring James Norton of Grantchester fame. The first series debuted on BBC One on 29 April 2014.Reviews from the media have been overwhelmingly positive, and the show has received 100% rating critic review on Rotten Tomatoes.However, some reviewers have criticised the show for its graphic content, especially in "Episode 3" and "Episode 4".

This torrent has all six episodes of Season 1. Subtitles are available as six separate files(not hardcoded)
